    <body>
        <div style="width:100%; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .75); margin-top: 5%; ">
            <a href="/">
                    <div style="margin-top: 1%; display:inline-block; border: .2em solid white; width: 10%;text-decoration: none; color: white; font-size: 1em;text-align: center;margin-left: 1%;">
                        <p style=" margin: 0%">
                            Back to Home
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            <div style="width: 60%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center; color: white;">
                
                <p style="font-size: 2vw; padding-top: 3%;">
                    <strong>Make An Appointment Today</strong>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Thanks for choosing me to join you on your journey to self discovery. Fill out the form below, and I'll get back to you within 36 hours.
                </p>
